21
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:08,240
Nekada je čak zgodno ne biti previše aktivan i previše se petljati i miješati, ulaziti u nešto.

22
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,200
Uay, ne.

23
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,320
Uay.

24
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:15,200
